 Hi Harry,
From "Without Guesswork":

http://www.thesamba.com/vw/archives/manuals/1965withoutguesswork/108-109.jpg

Best to use a HSS (High Speed Steel) tap, AND make sure it is either a nominal
size fit or lesser.  Most taps sold are over sized and you do not want those
wheel bolts (not nuts) to be just falling out.
E&B
